shows.title: Sidelined: The QB and Me
shows.plot_overview: Dallas, a burdened but headstrong dancer, is determined to get into the best dance school in the country—her late mother’s alma mater. However, that dream is suddenly derailed when the cheeky yet secretly grieving football star, Drayton, crashes into her life with a unique story of his own. Will the two of them be able to grow into their dreams together, or will their dreams be sidelined?

shows.title: Moonage Daydream
shows.plot_overview: A cinematic odyssey featuring never-before-seen footage exploring David Bowie's creative and musical journey.
